data.description:
Charming, well-maintained and updated! Great home for first time home buyers or a family that is looking for something easy to maintain. This 3 bedroom/2 bath home is located in a quiet and well-kept community close to schools, parks, and shopping. The entire home flows with beautiful flooring and an open kitchen that leads into the family
room which boasts a cozy fireplace and high ceilings. No rear neighbors and access to hiking
trails, the home backs up to beautiful St. John's Park! Conveniently located across the street from the community pool! This home is move in ready, contact your Realtor to schedule a private showing.
